        'Design-led boutique-appartementen voor koppels in Frigiliana en Nerja — gecureerde hosting, geverifieerde reviews, direct boeken.',
      robots: 'index, follow',
      canonical: 'auto'
    },
    sv: {
      title: 'AMARA Romantic Hideaways | Boutiqueboenden i Frigiliana & Nerja',
      description:
        'Designledda boutiquelägenheter för par i Frigiliana och Nerja — kurerad värdskap, verifierade omdömen, direktbokning.',
      robots: 'index, follow',
      canonical: 'auto'
    }
  },
  ogImage: '/images/hero-frigiliana.jpg'
};

type CopyRow = Record<AmaraLanguage, string>;

const copy = {
  heroSubtitle: {
    en: 'AMARA Romantic Hideaways',
    de: 'AMARA Romantic Hideaways',
    es: 'AMARA Romantic Hideaways',
    nl: 'AMARA Romantic Hideaways',
    sv: 'AMARA Romantic Hideaways'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  heroTitleHtml: {
    en: 'Design-led stays for couples<br />Frigiliana &amp; Nerja, Andalusia',
    de: 'Design-geführte Aufenthalte für Paare<br />Frigiliana &amp; Nerja, Andalusien',
    es: 'Estancias con diseño para parejas<br />Frigiliana y Nerja, Andalucía',
    nl: 'Designgedreven verblijven voor koppels<br />Frigiliana &amp; Nerja, Andalusië',
    sv: 'Designledda vistelser för par<br />Frigiliana &amp; Nerja, Andalusien'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  heroLead: {
    en: 'A place to arrive, exhale, and truly stay — not just pass through.',
    de: 'Ein Ort zum Ankommen, Durchatmen und wirklich Bleiben — nicht nur Durchreisen.',
    es: 'Un lugar para llegar, exhalar y quedarse de verdad — no solo pasar.',
    nl: 'Een plek om aan te komen, uit te ademen en echt te blijven — niet alleen door te reizen.',
    sv: 'En plats att komma till, andas ut och verkligen stanna — inte bara passera.'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  prose: {
    en: [
      'AMARA is a curated collection of private boutique apartments in the white village of Frigiliana, plus one calm seaside escape in Nerja. Created for guests who value privacy, atmosphere, and a slower rhythm of travel.',
      'Casa AMARA in Frigiliana dates back more than 800 years and was carefully restored in 2022. Today, it stands as one of the village icons — quietly woven into the fabric of Frigiliana itself.',
      'Award-winning. Consistently top-rated.<br />Direct booking available.'
    ],
    de: [
      'AMARA ist eine kuratierte Sammlung privater Boutique-Apartments im weißen Dorf Frigiliana plus einem ruhigen Küstenort in Nerja. Für Gäste, die Privatsphäre, Atmosphäre und ein langsameres Reisetempo schätzen.',
      'Casa AMARA in Frigiliana ist über 800 Jahre alt und wurde 2022 sorgfältig restauriert. Heute ist es eines der Dorfikonen — leise im Gefüge von Frigiliana verwoben.',
      'Preisgekrönt. Dauerhaft top bewertet.<br />Direktbuchung möglich.'
    ],
    es: [
      'AMARA es una colección curada de apartamentos boutique privados en el pueblo blanco de Frigiliana, más un refugio costero tranquilo en Nerja. Pensado para quienes valoran la privacidad, la atmósfera y un ritmo de viaje más pausado.',
      'Casa AMARA en Frigiliana tiene más de 800 años y fue restaurada con mimo en 2022. Hoy es uno de los iconos del pueblo — tejida con discreción en la vida de Frigiliana.',
      'Galardonada. Siempre muy valorada.<br />Reserva directa disponible.'
    ],
    nl: [
      'AMARA is een gecureerde collectie privé boutique-appartementen in het witte dorp Frigiliana, plus één rustige kustontsnapping in Nerja. Voor gasten die privacy, sfeer en een langzamer reisritme waarderen.',
      'Casa AMARA in Frigiliana is meer dan 800 jaar oud en werd in 2022 zorgvuldig gerestaureerd. Vandaag is het een van de dorpsiconen — onopvallend verweven met Frigiliana.',
      'Bekroond. Steeds top beoordeeld.<br />Direct boeken mogelijk.'
    ],
    sv: [
      'AMARA är en kurerad samling privata boutiquelägenheter i den vita byn Frigiliana, plus ett lugnt kustnära alternativ i Nerja. För gäster som värdesätter integritet, stämning och ett långsammare resande.',
      'Casa AMARA i Frigiliana är mer än 800 år gammal och restaurerades omsorgsfullt 2022. Idag är det en av byns ikoner — diskret vävd in i Frigilianas väv.',
      'Prisbelönt. Konsekvent topprankad.<br />Direktbokning finns.'
    ]
  } satisfies Record<AmaraLanguage, string[]>,
  ctaBook: {
    en: 'Check availability',
    de: 'Verfügbarkeit prüfen',
    es: 'Consultar disponibilidad',
    nl: 'Beschikbaarheid bekijken',
    sv: 'Se tillgänglighet'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  ctaAmenities: {
    en: 'Amenities & policies',
    de: 'Ausstattung & Richtlinien',
    es: 'Servicios y políticas',
    nl: 'Voorzieningen en beleid',
    sv: 'Bekvämligheter och policyer'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  trustBooking: {
    en: 'Booking.com Traveller Award',
    de: 'Booking.com Traveller Award',
    es: 'Booking.com Traveller Award',
    nl: 'Booking.com Traveller Award',
    sv: 'Booking.com Traveller Award'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  trustAirbnb: {
    en: '500+ verified Airbnb reviews',
    de: '500+ verifizierte Airbnb-Bewertungen',
    es: '500+ reseñas verificadas en Airbnb',
    nl: '500+ geverifieerde Airbnb-reviews',
    sv: '500+ verifierade Airbnb-recensioner'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  trustDirect: {
    en: 'Direct booking benefits',
    de: 'Vorteile der Direktbuchung',
    es: 'Ventajas de reserva directa',
    nl: 'Voordelen van direct boeken',
    sv: 'Fördelar med direktbokning'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  collectionTitle: {
    en: 'The AMARA collection',
    de: 'Die AMARA-Kollektion',
    es: 'La colección AMARA',
    nl: 'De AMARA-collectie',
    sv: 'AMARA-kollektionen'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  collectionIntro: {
    en: 'Each home follows the same hosting philosophy — they simply offer different ways to experience it.',
    de: 'Jedes Zuhause folgt derselben Hosting-Philosophie — sie bieten nur unterschiedliche Arten, sie zu erleben.',
    es: 'Cada hogar sigue la misma filosofía de acogida — solo ofrecen formas distintas de vivirla.',
    nl: 'Elk huis volgt dezelfde hostingfilosofie — ze bieden slechts verschillende manieren om die te ervaren.',
    sv: 'Varje hem följer samma värdskapsfilosofi — de erbjuder bara olika sätt att uppleva den.'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  reviewsEyebrow: {
    en: 'Guest-verified',
    de: 'Gastverifiziert',
    es: 'Verificado por huéspedes',
    nl: 'Door gasten geverifieerd',
    sv: 'Gästverifierat'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  reviewsHeadline: {
    en: 'Rated 4.95 out of 5 · 500+ verified guest reviews',
    de: '4,95 von 5 · 500+ verifizierte Gästebewertungen',
    es: '4,95 de 5 · 500+ reseñas verificadas',
    nl: '4,95 van 5 · 500+ geverifieerde reviews',
    sv: '4,95 av 5 · 500+ verifierade recensioner'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  reviewsBody: {
    en: 'Calm stays, terrace mornings, quiet nights, deep sleep — thoughtfully hosted.',
    de: 'Ruhige Aufenthalte, Terrassenmorgen, leise Nächte, tiefer Schlaf — durchdacht betreut.',
    es: 'Estancias tranquilas, mañanas en la terraza, noches en silencio, sueño profundo — con un cuidado meditado.',
    nl: 'Rustige verblijven, terrasochtenden, stille nachten, diepe slaap — doordacht gehost.',
    sv: 'Lugna vistelser, terrassmorgnar, tysta nätter, djup sömn — omsorgsfullt värdskap.'
  } satisfies CopyRow,
  reviewsCta: {
    en: 'Read all guest reviews',
    de: 'Alle Gästebewertungen lesen',
    es: 'Leer todas las reseñas',
    nl: 'Alle gastbeoordelingen lezen',
    sv: 'Läs alla gästrecensioner'
  } satisfies CopyRow
};

const t = <T extends Record<AmaraLanguage, string>>(row: T) => row[currentLang] ?? row.en;
const tArr = (row: Record<AmaraLanguage, string[]>) => row[currentLang] ?? row.en;

const trustLinks = [
  { token: 'about', label: 'About AMARA' },
  { token: 'reviews_hub', label: 'Guest Reviews' },
  { token: 'direct_booking_benefits', label: 'Direct Booking Benefits' }
];

const footerHighlights = [
  { token: 'amenities', label: t({ en: 'Amenities', de: 'Ausstattung', es: 'Servicios', nl: 'Voorzieningen', sv: 'Bekvämligheter' }) },
  { token: 'faq_general', label: t({ en: 'Stay FAQ', de: 'Aufenthalts-FAQ', es: 'FAQ de la estancia', nl: 'Verblijfs-FAQ', sv: 'FAQ för vistelsen' }) },
  { token: 'instagram', label: t({ en: 'Instagram', de: 'Instagram', es: 'Instagram', nl: 'Instagram', sv: 'Instagram' }) }
];

const featureChipsByLang: Record<AmaraLanguage, { label: string; note?: string }[]> = {
  en: [
    { label: 'Sea views', note: '(selected)' },
    { label: 'Large private terraces' },
    { label: 'Quiet locations' },
    { label: 'Premium bedding' },
    { label: 'Fast fibre WiFi' },
    { label: 'Climate control' }
  ],
  de: [
    { label: 'Meerblick', note: '(ausgew.)' },
    { label: 'Große private Terrassen' },
    { label: 'Ruhige Lagen' },
    { label: 'Premium-Bettwäsche' },
    { label: 'Schnelles Glasfaser-WLAN' },
    { label: 'Klimatisierung' }
  ],
  es: [
    { label: 'Vistas al mar', note: '(en parte)' },
    { label: 'Grandes terrazas privadas' },
    { label: 'Ubicaciones tranquilas' },
    { label: 'Ropa de cama premium' },
    { label: 'WiFi de fibra rápida' },
    { label: 'Climatización' }
  ],
  nl: [
    { label: 'Zeezicht', note: '(selectie)' },
    { label: 'Grote privéterrassen' },
    { label: 'Rustige locaties' },
    { label: 'Premium beddengoed' },
    { label: 'Snelle glasvezel-WiFi' },
    { label: 'Klimaatregeling' }
  ],
  sv: [
    { label: 'Havsutsikt', note: '(utvalt)' },
    { label: 'Stora privata terrasser' },
    { label: 'Tysta lägen' },
    { label: 'Premium sängkläder' },
    { label: 'Snabbt fiber-WiFi' },
    { label: 'Klimatkontroll' }
  ]
};

const apartments = [
  {
    token: 'farah' as const,
    imageSrc: 'https://l.icdbcdn.com/oh/3c79ee18-d231-4066-bbce-1b20c4732057.jpg',
    imageAlt: 'AMARA Farah – Romantic Boutique Stay in Frigiliana for couples',
    meta: 'Frigiliana • 2 guests',
    title: 'AMARA Farah – Boutique Retreat',
    description: 'A romantic boutique room with character — ideal for shorter trips.',
    ctaLabel: 'Explore Farah'
  },
  {
    token: 'lounis' as const,
    imageSrc: 'https://l.icdbcdn.com/oh/882b7732-0b8a-4d00-b9af-16271f78d09e.jpg',
    imageAlt: 'AMARA Lounis – Historic Frigiliana Apartment with terrace',
    meta: 'Frigiliana • 2 guests',
    title: 'AMARA Lounis – Historic Apartment',
    description: 'Historic charm with terrace time and a sense of space.',
    ctaLabel: 'Explore Apartment'
  },
  {
    token: 'zaid' as const,
    imageSrc: 'https://l.icdbcdn.com/oh/392c7773-50bf-4814-955d-da26457f6440.jpg',
    imageAlt: 'AMARA Zaid – Frigiliana Apartment with private terrace',
    meta: 'Frigiliana • 2 guests',
    title: 'AMARA Zaid – Terrace Apartment',
    description: 'A calm retreat with terrace — made for slow mornings.',
    ctaLabel: 'Explore Apartment'
  },
  {
    token: 'maha' as const,
    imageSrc: 'https://l.icdbcdn.com/oh/3e9884fa-4453-4aa8-8dae-fb54d6a87456.jpg',
    imageAlt: 'AMARA Maha – Romantic Penthouse Apartment in Frigiliana Old Town',
    meta: 'Frigiliana • 2 guests',
    title: 'AMARA Maha – Old Town Apartment',
    description: 'A terrace apartment designed for lingering in the white village.',
    ctaLabel: 'Explore Apartment'
  },
  {
    token: 'playa' as const,
    imageSrc: 'https://l.icdbcdn.com/oh/46e112f1-729d-4a76-9c7a-df53cb2e2626.jpg',
    imageAlt: 'AMARA Playa – Coastal Nerja Apartment near the beach with sea view',
    meta: 'Nerja • 2 guests',
    title: 'AMARA Playa – Nerja Beach Apartment',
    description: 'A relaxed seaside base for couples who want the sea close by.',
    ctaLabel: 'Explore Apartment'
  },
  {
    token: 'casa' as const,
    imageSrc: 'https://l.icdbcdn.com/oh/aa11c018-1653-4e74-9bcc-831dc0f8a3e7.jpg',
    imageAlt: 'AMARA Ocean View Penthouse – Family & Surf holiday rental Tarifa',
    meta: 'Tarifa • family stay',
    title: 'AMARA Ocean View Penthouse',
    description: 'A spacious home for surfers and families — intentionally different.',
    ctaLabel: 'Explore Penthouse'
  }
];
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo} pageLang={currentLang} footerHighlights={footerHighlights}>
  <Navigation
    currentLang={currentLang}
    brandName="AMARA"
    links={trustLinks}
    variant="trust"
    languageToken="romantic_hideaways"
  />

  <div class="am-root bg-surface min-h-screen relative overflow-hidden" data-am-page="romantic-hideaways">
    <div class="am-wrap w-full max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 pb-20">
      <section class="pt-8 pb-16 md:pb-24 relative z-10">
        <TrustHero
          subtitle={t(copy.heroSubtitle)}
          title={t(copy.heroTitleHtml)}
          lead={t(copy.heroLead)}
          ctaLinks={[]}
        />

        <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-5 mt-8 am-text-body text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          {
            tArr(copy.prose).map((html) => (
              <p set:html={html} />
            ))
          }
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 mt-8">
          <a class="am-btn am-btn--primary" href={resolveLink('book', currentLang)}>{t(copy.ctaBook)}</a>
          <a class="am-btn am-btn--ghost" href={resolveLink('amenities', currentLang)}>{t(copy.ctaAmenities)}</a>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-8 gap-y-4 mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border-subtle am-text-body text-on-surface-variant"
          id="direct-booking"
        >
          <span>{t(copy.trustBooking)}</span>
          <span>{t(copy.trustAirbnb)}</span>
          <a class="am-inline-link" href={resolveLink('direct_booking_benefits', currentLang)}>{t(copy.trustDirect)}</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section
        id="booking"
        class="py-16 md:py-24 border-t border-border-subtle relative z-10"
        aria-labelledby="collection-title"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 max-w-3xl">
          <h2 id="collection-title" class="am-text-title tracking-tight">{t(copy.collectionTitle)}</h2>
          <p class="am-text-body text-on-surface-variant">{t(copy.collectionIntro)}</p>
        </div>

        <ApartmentGrid>
          {
            apartments.map((apt) => (
              <ApartmentCard
                href={resolveLink(apt.token, currentLang)}
                imageSrc={apt.imageSrc}
                imageAlt={apt.imageAlt}
                meta={apt.meta}
                title={apt.title}
                description={apt.description}
                ctaLabel={apt.ctaLabel}
              />
            ))
          }
        </ApartmentGrid>
      </section>

      <GuestReviewsSummary
        eyebrow={t(copy.reviewsEyebrow)}
        headline={t(copy.reviewsHeadline)}
        body={t(copy.reviewsBody)}
        reviewsHref={resolveLink('reviews_hub', currentLang)}
        reviewsCtaLabel={t(copy.reviewsCta)}
        features={featureChipsByLang[currentLang]}
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
